ead Teacher</a>. Feb 26, 2018</p><p><hr size=\"1\"><a  href=\"http://traffic.libsyn.com/principalmatters/PMP103.mp3\">William D. Parker: PMP:103 Standing Back Up When You Feel Knocked Down</a>. Feb 21, 2018</p><p><hr size=\"1\"><a  href=\"http://traffic.libsyn.com/principalmatters/PMP102.mp3\">William D. Parker: PMP:102 Four Essentials for Advancing in Your Leadership</a>. Feb 14, 2018</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<hr size=\"1\">Listen to  <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/archive.cgi?page=edradio.htm\">previous broadcasts</a> (also in <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/archive.cgi?page=playlist.m3u\">.m3u format</a>; will play in your audio player)\r\n\r\n<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Ed Radio Feeds</h2><br/>\r\n<hr/><p><b>All in the Mind</b>  <br/> RSS 0.91. Last Updated: Tue, 27 Jun 2017 00:00:00 +0000 <br/>\r\n Programme exploring the limits and potential of the human mind \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<hr/><p><b>AskPat: Your Online Business, Blogging, Marketing and Lifestyle Design Questions Answered Daily!</b>  <br/> Twitter,. Last Updated: Thu, 08 Sep 2016 05:40:04 -0400 <br/>\r\n <p>I&rsquo;m Pat Flynn, a regular guy who happens to be a successful online entrepreneur. You may know me from my other podcast, Smart Passive Income, which is consistently ranked as a #1 business podcast. I love hearing from my fans, and boy do they love sending me questions :) That&rsquo;s why I&rsquo;ve started the AskPat podcast. AskPat is a brand new, DAILY podcast. Each episode features an actual question submitted from someone like you! I won\'t be able to answer everyone\'s question, but I\'ll do my best to get through as many of them as I can. Now, plug in those headphones because it&rsquo;s time to learn together about online business, entrepreneurship, internet marketing, audience building, passive income, blogging, list building, virtual assistants, startups, search engine optimization, email marketing and so much more. #askpat</p> \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<hr/><p><b>BBC Inside Science</b>  <br/> RSS 0.91. La